Pete Davidson has been receiving the heat since his relationship with Ariana Grande ended. The comedian, Pete, said on his Instagram post that he just couldn’t keep quiet any longer about the constant harassment. Ariana and Pete broke their engagement in October 2018.    A post shared by  Pete Davidson (@petedavidson) on Dec 3, 2018 at 9:30am PST The Instagram post comes up not too far from when Ariana Grande covered her Pete-inspired tattoo on her foot. The new tattoo replacement is a tribute to Ariana’s ex-Mac Miller. 